				<td colspan="2"><span>To do this efficiently requires you camp east AND west wall golems. You can get spider adds with no prob but if you get a lightcrawler-thing (crystalline crawler) run away a bit and mem a few chants to kill it first. ANYHOO yeah, golems take about 15 min to aoe kite down and you can do em in groups of 5 (about 1 gold aa) or 25(about 1 aa) in the same amount of time. dont use snare because you will get smacked. I find the right amount is where with particles turned on my comp slows down a tiny bit when the pulse hits (about 25 mobs).
<br />

<br />
EDIT: Find yourself a GOOD stringed instrument, the point-purchased one from EC is what I use (510 points, 2.6 mod and primary equippable)</span></td>
